data.name: ReadCseOrganizationOffice
data.value: select T3.COG_CHILD_CODE, T3.COG_CHILD_TYPE, T2.OFFICE_ID, T2.COG_TYPE_CODE, T2.COG_CODE, T2.OFF_OFFICE from CKT_CSE_ORG_RELATN T3 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OFFICE T2 with(readuncommitted) on T3.COG_CHILD_TYPE = 'J' and T3.REASON_CODE = 'JC' and T3.COG_PARENT_TYPE = T2.COG_TYPE_CODE and T3.COG_PARENT_CODE = T2.COG_CODE where exists ( select * from CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T5 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_ASSIGN_CASE T6 with(readuncommitted) on T5.EFFECTIVE_DATE = T6.OSP_DATE and T5.ROLE_CODE = T6.OSP_CODE and T5.OFF_GENERATED_ID = T6.OFF_ID and T5.SPD_GENERATED_ID = T6.SPD_ID and T6.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate and T6.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate and T6.CAS_NO = @casNo where T2.OFFICE_ID = T5.OFF_GENERATED_ID )
